title: "The GUAN Framework: Cognitive Copilot + Multi-LLM Orchestration Architecture"
abstract: >-
  A file-based, git-native framework for building persistent AI cognitive profiles
  (GUAN Cards, Challenge Contract Protocol, Tiered Loading) and orchestrating work
  across multiple LLM platforms (Context Compiler, 70-20-10 Distribution Rule,
  Patch-Only Delegation). Developed by GUAN through iterative multi-model
  consultation across Claude, GPT, Gemini, and DeepSeek. March 2026.
